workflow:
-- use collect.py to gather initial .tif
-- convert tif to latlon using gdal_warp
-- use extract_chunk.py to get the particular rectangular region of data you want
-- plot.py will plot this region if wanted.
-- use to mesh to project to meters and build the meshes.
